data.description: Adorable Custom Built Ranch home with 3 bedroom and  2 bathrooms nestled away on just under an acre! Take the long tree lined driveway back to your oasis. This charming brick home features luxurious landscaping which you can enjoy from either the large covered front porch or the screened in patio on the back. This beautiful home features hardwood floors throughout, crown molding, formal dining room, stainless steel appliances to include a double oven. Enjoy fresh water with the reverse osmosis system installed on every sink. HVAC replace in 2018 &  Roof was replaced in 2020. This home will not stay on the market long, located in the desired Grays Creek School district and close to shopping, dining, and the Ft. Liberty. Schedule you viewing today.  Seller offering VA assumable loan at 3%.
